<!channel> hey everyone! I’m looking to compile a top 10 list from all of you like I did last year. If you don’t remember, or weren’t around last year, basically pick 10 new cards that were printed this last year (rivals, dom, battlebond, M19, commander 2018, guilds of rav) For each of the cards you pick, write a sentence or two why you like it so much. Also, include a short blurb about what articles you normally write (maybe it’ll bring your articles new readers).

If you can have these to me by December 14th to give me a bit of time to put it together, that’d be great. You can either message me directly on here or email it to me at <mailto:acummings@wcr7.org|acummings@wcr7.org>
